he URI is retrieved as a string, it wouldn't contain plain blank spaces.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Right now we're in an awkward state where URIs can be stored with plain blank spaces, which is disallowed by <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3986#appendix-A\" rel=\"nofollow\">RFC 3986</a> but is needed by <code>ign-fuel-tools</code>.</p>\n<p>It would be more appropriate to support encoding / decoding of the URI, so when the URI is retrieved as a string, it wouldn't contain plain blank spaces.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2018-08-02T21:39:23.419765+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2018-08-02T21:39:23.419765+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 38}